column84:
The fostowing improvement have been performed for the CAD Resources:
- "CAD design files" taxonomy available in CCC under Layout & Diagrams folder and the resources are displayed on CAD Resources tab at Product folder level;
- any CAD resources can be categorized as License Agreement or Thirdy party to astow a different kind of validation;
- download internet/extranet flow of any CAD resources with a License Agreement are treated like Software download process (email validation, cookie popup, ...);
- logic implemented to verify the existence of the Thirdy party hosted resources through validation and unique RPN association;
- ensured CAD License Agreement tracking through Adobe Campaign;
- Thirdy Party hosted resources are available on CAD Resources as a link;
- button for multiple resource download removed from CAD Resources tab;
- CAD resources are displayed according to the fostowing option:
   - CAD resources not License Agreements and not Third party;
   - CAD resources License Agreements;
   - CAD resources Third party.

